# 13. 静かに、あたたかく

Mafuyu: Hmm? What's my computer doing?
Mafuyu: Looks like a music file. Who sent it to me?
Mafuyu: Huh?! Why did the screen just flash?!
Mafuyu: Where...am I?
Miku: ...
Mafuyu: Who are you?
Miku: I'm Miku.
Mafuyu: Miku, as in...Hatsune Miku?
Miku: So this was how Mafuyu and this SEKAI's version of me met for the first time...
Miku: (She doesn't know who the real her is, and desperately wants to find out...)
Miku: (But that's much easier said than done...)
Miku: (At this point in time, Mafuyu has no idea what her true feelings are.)
Miku: (Simultaneously, this SEKAI's me wasn't really sure how she was going to help her.)
Miku: (But still...)
Mafuyu: Miku.
Miku: Mafuyu, you're here...
Mafuyu: *Nod*
Mafuyu: I thought writing a song would help me discover my true feelings, but I'm still having trouble...
Miku: I see...
Mafuyu: This SEKAI really is empty.
Mafuyu: But I understand why...
Mafuyu: Because it's based on my feelings...
Mafuyu: ...
Mafuyu: Do you think I'll ever know...?
Miku: Don't worry.
Miku: I'll help you find the real you.
Mafuyu: Okay...
Mafuyu: Um, Miku...?
Miku: Yes?
Mafuyu: Can I stay here for a little while longer...?
Miku: Of course.
Miku: This is your SEKAI after all, Mafuyu.
Mafuyu: Thank you...
Miku: (That's right...)
Miku: (This SEKAI ends up becoming a very important place for Mafuyu.)
Miku: (Naturally, for this version of me as well...)
[K]: <I listened to your mix of that song, Yuki. Thank you for doing that.>
Mafuyu: Oh...
Mafuyu: <Thank you, K. What did you think...?>
[K]: <It was much deeper than I was expecting. I thought I was being tossed into this dark and quiet chasm of despair.>
[K]: <But I also felt like I was searching for the light. That was really well done...>
Mafuyu: <Hehe. That was present in the demo you made, K. All I did was add a few more sounds on top of that...>
[K]: <Still, I believe you've helped make it a lot better. So, Yuki, thank you.>
Mafuyu: <You're welcome...>
Mafuyu: (I felt something while listening to this song too, but I still haven't found what I'm looking for...)
Mafuyu: (But someday...)
Mafuyu: (Someday, I'll find...)
Teacher: I really appreciate you always helping me, Asahina, but I feel bad about making you do this during your lunch break.
Mafuyu: No, this is nothing. You needed me to carry these papers over to the classroom, yes?
Teacher: Yes, that would be incredibly helpful!
Teacher: Also, if you have time...
Mafuyu's Mother: I heard from your teacher that you've decided to become a class representative, Mafuyu. Is that true?
Mafuyu: Yes, it is... Everyone said that I should take the job.
Mafuyu's Mother: Oh, I'm so proud of you. Be sure to do your very best, okay?
Mafuyu's Mother: But try not to be too helpful either, since those receiving your assistance won't be able to grow as individuals.
Mafuyu: Hehe. I'll be careful. Thanks for the warning, Mom.
Miku: Are you feeling okay, Mafuyu...?
Mafuyu: Miku...
Mafuyu: I'm okay... I think...
Mafuyu: But I'm so tired...
Mafuyu: I've looked and looked, but still haven't found any answers...
Mafuyu: This void inside of me just keeps growing and growing.
Mafuyu: Now... I just want to disappear...
Miku: Mafuyu...
Miku: But your true feelings...
Mafuyu: My true feelings...?
Mafuyu: If I can't find them after searching this much...
Mafuyu: Then I can't help but wonder if they exist at all...
Miku: B-But...
Mafuyu: I'm done.
Mafuyu: More to the point, Miku...
Mafuyu: I just want to stay in this SEKAI forever.
Miku: Oh...
Miku: ...
Miku: ...
Miku: I want to help Mafuyu find her true feelings...
Miku: But that won't happen at this rate...
Miku: What do I do...?
Miku: Oh...
Miku: This song...
Miku: It's the one by that person Mafuyu's been working with...
Miku: This SEKAI is completely empty, with the exception of this song...
Miku: Then...
Miku: The person who made this song might be able to help find the real Mafuyu.
Miku: I think I'll go see her...
Miku: For Mafuyu's sake...
Miku: Thank you.
Miku: For trying so hard all by yourself in this empty SEKAI, just for her.
Miku: For doing your best to keep her feelings safe.
Miku: ...?
Miku: I know you can...
Miku: I can't do anything to help...
Miku: But I'll always be watching over you.
Miku: Now and forever.
Miku: Oh...
Miku: What happened...?
Miku: Just now... I felt all this warmth...
